Package: palladin-runtime
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCHITECTURE@
Maintainer: Palladin Security <security@palladin.io>
Depends: systemd (>= 252), polkitd, passwd, util-linux
Homepage: https://palladin.io
Description: Hardened native runtime broker for dedicated Palladin Agent UIDs
 This optional system package installs the Linux Hardened broker and one-shot
 executor boundary. The public npm package remains an unprivileged launcher.
